component.name: RunManager
component.selected: Attach to Unity Editor.Attach to Unity Editor

task.summary: added rocket compound object. various materials for different parts of rocket.
added rocket input handler. added 'Thrust', 'RotateLeft' and 'RotateRight' virtual keys.
moved code that thrusts rocket to fixed update. now rocket can move thrust upwards when `space` is pressed
added obstacles. constrain rocket movement to x,y axis. constrain rotation to only z axis. freeze physics rotation while manually rotating
changed materials for the various objects in the scene. created obstacles for testing. now rocket can distinguish between collisions with obstacles and landing pad.
created obstacle prefabs. landing pad prefab. created another level.

player has dead/alive states. scriptable object event system created. events generated when player either dead or reaches end of current level. on death, first level loaded. On reach end of level, next level loaded.
added death and success afx. created new states to represent thrusting, not thrusting and level complete. audio is chosen based on state.
added oscillator obstacle that can move. uses kinematic rigidbody.
added debugging key presses to disable rocket collisions and move to next level. `l` to move to the next level and `c` to disable collisions on the rocket.
created new script to handle debug key presses. created new scriptable object variable for disabling/enabling player collision.
